[It is important to investigate the source of infection. One possibility -- if the sausages were manufactured in Corsica -- is that meat from wild boar was illegally used without proper veterinary inspection. Another possibility is that meat with _Trichinella_ was imported and used -- for instance, horse meat. - Mod.EP

